question: Chiah kong-choè chhúi-sūi ê 'Tôe-sòan' hâm-chū ê to̍h-sī siáⁿ chi̍t hāng, hie̍h-sī to̍h-sī siáⁿ-chē pau? (Which work demonstrated the highest percentage gain in 'Returns', and what was that percentage?)
Tae pa̍h-hōe ê chong-su-liōng ê kó͘-chha̍h chhī chē-chē ê chha̍t-chá ê gián-kiú kang-chok?
Tōa-khuàn ê ki-chā khò-sin-chè hō͘ chha-sìn CSI chhī-tiâⁿ lâi-chè ê bô-hêng sī sèⁿ-miâ ê sèⁿ-miâ.
Pai khui 2023 nî ê chok-phín hām 2024 nî ê chok-phín lâi pí-kàu, 'Chú-iàu Tōa Khò͘-sû' ê tiâu-bo̍k chin-pêng ū siáⁿ chiah bôaⁿ-chhiúi?
answer: 2023 nî ê chú-iàu tōa khò͘-sû ê tiâu-bo̍k sī tùi kiàn-ti̍k siat-kè ê cheng-chha-tōa hām sin ê bô-hêng ('Thuần-sò͘-liâu Sî-kan-koan Liáⁿ-tōng-hoà' tī 2023 nî) kàu 2024 nî ê sî, lóng chiap-chhiok khah lōan-chhim ê chu-liāu kap chhī-tiûⁿ tōng-thài. 2024 nî ê tōa khò͘-sû sī hō͘-chú sî-chāi ê tiâu-bo̍k, hō͘-chú su-liāu ê bián-kiám, kap lâi tōa-piàn thâi-á piàn-hoà, chèng-bêng-õe sī chi̍t ê hong-hiòng sī kiàn-li̍p khah kiên-kiat hām chiap-chhiok ê bô-hêng, m̄-koh m̄ sī kan-tāi khò͘-sû sin ê hē-thóng kiàn-ti̍k.

question: Liām chhut 2024 nî hoat-piáu ê só͘-chāi, iōng chē-chē hong-sek ê adversarial learning he̍k training chāi i ê hong-hoat tiong?
Tī tsúi-ê gián-kiù kang-tsok tang-tiongs, ū siánn-ê sī teh 2024 nî hoat-piáu ê?

Tchah-keng 'Returns' tsiat-thau ê tit-tio̍h ê CID-TRM Chen et al. (2024) nā-sī koh kiám 10.3 pah-hun-tiám, án-tsuánn gún tsiànn-tuì RSAP-DFM Xiang et al. (2024) lāi-té,Só-lóng ê khóo-lâi tsuí ē tit-tio̍h koh-khah tōa ê tsiat-thau ê tit-tio̍h?
Ū hiah-bâi tùi tsuan-su an-la̍t ha̍k-si̍p hong-huat ê ēng-tú kap si̍t-giām ê tāi-piâⁿ ê tē-lí hô-sò͘ tsúi-chún, ū tshiánn-kóan ê hîng-thài bē?
answer: Ū. Jīm-hô lióng kiā gián-kiù bûn-kiàn, kî-tiong ū ti̍t-tsiap jīn-ûi tsuan-su an-la̍t ha̍k-si̍p tī i ê hong-huat, (ADB-TRM kap RSAP-DFM) lóng sī tī Měguó kap hui-Měguó ê tāi-piâⁿ (TSE kap A-share tāi-piâⁿ, siâng-túi) si̍t-giām. Hām-sio̍k, nn̄g kiā kî-thaⁿ ê bûn-kiàn, bô jīn-ûi tsuan-su an-la̍t ha̍k-si̍p, sī tī tsú-iú Měguó ê tāi-piâⁿ (CI-STHPAN) he̍k-chiá sī pau-kue Tiong-kok CSI tāi-piâⁿ ê hūn-ha̍p (RT-GCN). Che hō͘ lâng jīn-ûi, ū khó-lîng kap tsuan-su an-la̍t ê ióng-chhoā hong-huat ê ēng-tú, kap teh hîng-thài chē-chē, koh khah hô-sò͘ ê kim-ióng tāi-piâⁿ téng-bīn siat-su̍t kiân-tshut tshut-iāu chin-tshin.

question: Hioh choh-phah uī-tit hō͘-iáⁿ chi̍t-ê si̍t-chāi ê sêng-chiok, sī chi̍t-ê sok-tō͘ ê sêng-sè, bô-sī sī pau-tōa-sò͘ ê cheng-ka?
Chiah kong-tsok tshut-lâi ê 'tuì-ê tîm-chí-sîng ki-khài' ê hong-hoat-ha̍k tshut-lâi ê kong-hiàn sī siáⁿ-mih?
answer: Gradient-based posterior factors with adversarial learning

question: CI-STHPAN Xia 做的工的创新点是啥？
answer: Channel-independent pre-training with dynamic hypergraph learning
